title: Google\Cloud\AIPlatform\V1\TensorboardExperiment
name: TensorboardExperiment
description:
A TensorboardExperiment is a group of TensorboardRuns, that are typically the results of a training job run, in a Tensorboard.

Generated from protobuf message google.cloud.aiplatform.v1.TensorboardExperiment

Extends Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message
